    h2.option Here you can manage the various BetterTTV options. Click On or Off to toggle settings.
#bttvAbout(style="display:none;")
  .aboutHalf
    img.bttvAboutIcon(src="https://cdn.betterttv.net/style/logos/mascot.png")
